{"id":151543,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/希腊出售16亿欧元国债/","date":"2011-05-10T21:30:34Z","modified":"2011-05-10T21:30:34Z","title":"希腊出售16亿欧元国债","content":"<div>\n<p>雅典<br />债务危机中的希腊再次从投资者手中获得16亿欧元贷款。但这一债券的偿还期限仅为6个月，利息为4.88%。希腊财政部对利息水平表示满意。欧盟委员会、欧洲央行和国际货币基金组织目前正在雅典审核该国的削减开支情况。欧盟货币专员雷恩表示，审核结束后将作出新的决定。据报道，希腊有望在现有的1100亿欧元援助款之外再获得600亿欧元，以避免国家破产。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15065848%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%B8%8C%E8%85%8A%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE16%E4%BA%BF%E6%AC%A7%E5%85%83%E5%9B%BD%E5%80%BA\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}